Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬間…只要一瞬間就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能夠打破這個快攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果准鏡沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我親手殺死他們的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須承受 並且不斷思考這個問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我能做的最低限度的贖罪 我現在是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人現在 正在努力將自己的話付諸實踐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用親手阻止代表SAO黑暗面的 名為「死槍」的犯罪者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(872,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到這一點並不是因為桐人很強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是他能夠接受自己的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時而煩惱 時而痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是即使如此 仍舊能夠繼續向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼…我能做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.97,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(640,543)}幽靈子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續這樣出汗的話 會有脫水的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途下線一次…是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟不管我們在這裏說什麼 桐人也聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在嚴重脫水的情況發生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AmuSphere應該會自動切斷遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 就在觀察一陣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請握住爸爸的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的手的溫度 一定可以傳遞到爸爸那裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手沒辦法觸及那邊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把我…請連帶著我的份也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯的溫度 也一定可以傳達到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起為爸爸 為桐人加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊桐人 為了那些相信著你的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠保護你的身後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實 是拒絕了知道這傢伙名字的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再次和他們扯上關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其實這種事本身就是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是強裝出一幅已經忘記了的樣子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是自欺欺人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得…在討伐戰之前的會議上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙薩！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅眼的沙薩！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條預測線 是詩乃根據她自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經驗 靈感 以及全身鬥志所發射的幻影子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後一擊 我絕不能辜負她的「幽靈子彈」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有…結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人…不會讓你…結束掉這一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 已經結束了 沙薩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同夥我們也會馬上找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「微笑棺木」的殺人行為就此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(432,670)}Laughing Coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該讓大會結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「死槍」已經倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(536,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要對你下手的他的同夥也肯定藏匿了蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就算現在登出了應該也沒有什麼危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防萬一 記得馬上去報警
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算我播了110 該怎麼解釋現狀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的也對…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的委託人好歹也是個公務員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去麻煩下他也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能在這裏問你的真實姓名和住址呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行的 我告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名是朝田詩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住址是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太巧了 我現在潛行的地方就在你附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼要不我登出之後就去找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你願意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個值得信任的朋友就住在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我登出了以後就和委託人聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他派警察過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先別管這個 你就不和我說下你的個人情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名叫桐谷和人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐谷和人 所以才叫桐人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是很隨便的命名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好意思說我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 為了登出 我們得先把這個BOB做個了斷先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要像昨天那樣以決鬥來分出高下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這不是已經遍體鱗傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算贏了這樣的你 我也一點都不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負就留到下次BOB大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 就讓我們結束這場BOB吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一定要有一個人HP歸零才能決定優勝者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說第一屆BOB是兩人同時獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因在於 應該獲勝的人不小心中了『手榴彈大禮』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手榴彈大禮？那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然「死槍」的被害者是2人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(547,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 共犯也有2人以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直蠢爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田 你在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 無論如何都想給你慶祝奪冠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買了這個來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 真心恭喜你奪冠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厲害啊朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩乃 你終於成了GGO最強的槍手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是朝田的話 終有一天能當上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田有著其他人沒有的 真正的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…你和我說過的吧 會等我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說了吧 只要我等下去的話 總有一天會屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 所以我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會一直陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不用依靠那種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會一直…一生保護…你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新…新川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田 我喜歡你 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的詩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的哦…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田不可以背叛我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新…川…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以動的哦 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個注射器裏的東西一進入身體的話 肌肉就會無法運動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心肺很快就會停止運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注射器？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打了某種藥物吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為我家開醫院的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸也約好了考進醫學專業 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是另外一個「死槍」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(763,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…挺厲害啊 看穿了「死槍」的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(769,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯哦 我就是「死槍」的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(687,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這麼說 在這次的大賽之前 是我操作Sterben的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 只有今天讓我來干現實這邊的活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟不能讓其他的男人來碰朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是兄弟也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄…兄弟？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在SAO裏加入殺人工會的 是新川的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不會丟下朝田你自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還 還來得及 還能重來的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去上補習班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要當醫生的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西已經怎麼樣都行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論父母還是學校那幫人都是無可救藥的蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能在GGO裏當上最強的話就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫ZEXD的人渣 說什麼敏系最強的謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GGO明明是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此我捨棄了現實的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就殺了ZXED嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 為了讓「死槍」成為GGO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(660,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是所有VRMMO中最強的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比他更好的祭品了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 我對這無聊的現實已經毫無眷戀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新川…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們一起去像GGO一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更奇幻的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們在那裏得到重生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結為夫婦一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起冒險 生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們成為一體吧 朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 朝田 真美 太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…我的…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直…一直都好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從在學校聽說朝田你遇到的那個事件以來 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用真的手槍擊斃罪犯的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找遍全日本也只有朝田你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過吧 朝田你是真的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在塑造「死槍」時我選擇了54式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(598,670)}Death Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是我憧憬的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你 愛你 比任何人都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…什麼都不想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想感知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一定…不是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還讓你來救我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你白跑一趟 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆下線後我去找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他真的過來 也會遭遇危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已經沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們至今為止只會關注自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會為了自己而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在說這些也許已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在最後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也試著為了他人而戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝…朝田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…朝田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…朝田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝田…朝田…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 詩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 一小步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:13.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}そう、強くなりたいと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:16.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,525)}悲しみを超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:31.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}変わることない過去に何度も背を向けてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:38.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}誰にも見せられない傷を隠したまま ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}溢れだしたこの痛みは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}全て一人で抱きしめる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}いつか消える温もりなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:53.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}一つもいらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:56.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:23:01.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}そう、強くなりたいと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:07.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}暗闇をかける孤独な星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:15.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}心深く沈めた弱くて脆い自分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:19.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}言葉にできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:22.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}声にもならなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:27.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}きっと誰にも見つからないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:32.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,825)}ただ 、光を待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:13.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}沒錯 我祈願能變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:16.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,525)}去超越悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:31.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}對著一成不變的過去 無數次轉過身去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:38.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}藏著無法給任何人看的傷疤 一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}溢出來的這份傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}全都自己抱著不放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}如果是終有一天會消失的溫暖
